body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information. As part of the conversation, the customer should ask two questions.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should cover two or three topics, have back and forth between the parties, and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello! My name is Tyler Wood and I'm a customer service representative at SafeShield Insurance Agency. How can I assist you today? May I have your name please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hello Tyler, my name is Brenda Ross.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Brenda! To better assist you, could you provide me with your date of birth and your policy number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, my date of birth is the twenty fifth of February, nineteen seventy five. And my policy number is five zero zero two three one seven.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for providing that information, Brenda. How can I help you today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I have a question about the coverage for rental cars. Does my policy include rental car reimbursement?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Yes, Brenda. Our policy does offer rental car reimbursement. Is there anything else you would like to know?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Thank you for clarifying that. I also wanted to inquire about the process for filing a claim. How should I go about it?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: You're welcome, Brenda. To file a claim, you can either visit our website and submit it online or contact our claims department directly. We can assist you with that. Thank you for your questions and for reaching out to us. Is there anything else I can help you with today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, that will be all for now. Thank you for your assistance, Tyler.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: You're welcome, Brenda. Thank you for choosing SafeShield Insurance Agency. Have a wonderful day!
